metadata.name: 1,093 TrueFANZ #1
metadata.description: Thank you for being one of the first 1,093 TRUEFanz! Your SuperPOWERED support of the $ADHD coin and community has changed my life and so many others! I was inspired to take a different approach to building this community thanks to the 1K true fan essay by Kevin Kelly and because my hockey number is 93 I figured I would add my own twist. Perks to come for all those holding this NFT but till then I just want to send you a SuperPOWERED THANK YOU! - Fanzo WE > Me
